In the Bedroom;;81;;93;;R;;Summertime on the coast of Maine, "In the Bedroom" centers on the inner dynamics of a family in transition. Matt Fowler (Tom Wilkinson) is a doctor practicing in his native Maine and is married to New York born Ruth Fowler (Sissy Spacek), a music teacher. He is involved in a love affair with a local single mother (Marisa Tomei). As the beauty of Maine's brief and fleeting summer comes to an end, these characters find themselves in the midst of unimaginable tragedy.;;Drama;;Todd Field;;2001;;Sissy Spacek,Tom Wilkinson,Nick Stahl,Marisa Tomei,William Mapother,William Wise,Celia Weston,Karen Allen;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_the_bedroom